Package executor.parser

Class CreationCommandParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • executor.parser.CreationCommandParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandParser
    public class CreationCommandParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandParser
    Implements a CommandParser which process taskCreation commands. Such commands include "todo", "event", and "bye". In particular it checks for the number of arguments corresponding to the provided command.
